      <p>MM SEO is the freelance SEO consultancy of Mithul Mistry — a senior SEO specialist with 18 years of experience across agency and in-house digital environments in the UK. Based in Marple, Stockport, MM SEO serves clients across Manchester, Cheshire, and nationally.</p>
      <p>MM SEO operates as a direct-access, solo consultancy. Clients work one-to-one with Mithul — there are no junior account managers, no subcontracted work, and no agency overhead. The proposition is specialist-level SEO at a price point accessible to SMEs who would otherwise be underserved by larger agencies.</p>
      <p>The consultancy has delivered measurable results across eCommerce, legal services, hospitality, financial services, and professional services — with documented case studies including 552% organic revenue growth and 125% traffic increases for retail clients within six months.</p>
