      <p>His technical depth covers crawl auditing, Core Web Vitals, GA4, Google Search Console, Screaming Frog, Sitebulb, and Ahrefs. His strategic output includes bespoke keyword research, content architecture, digital PR link building, and persona-led SEO strategy. He has delivered campaigns for eCommerce brands, hospitality groups, professional services firms, and local businesses.</p>
