      <p class="intro-text">MM SEO provides a full suite of search engine optimisation services. All work is carried out directly by Mithul Mistry.</p>
      <div class="cards-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>SEO Strategy</h3>
          <p>Bespoke SEO roadmaps built around business objectives, competitive landscape, and current site performance. Covers audit, keyword research, prioritisation, and phased delivery planning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Technical SEO</h3>
          <p>Full technical audits covering crawlability, indexation, site speed, Core Web Vitals, structured data, mobile usability, and internal architecture. Tools: Screaming Frog, Sitebulb, PageSpeed Insights, GSC.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Keyword Research</h3>
          <p>Search intent mapping, competitor keyword gap analysis, long-tail opportunity identification, and content architecture planning aligned to commercial objectives.</p>
        </div>
